move-mouse (4.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial Linux port from Windows WPF/.NET Framework.
  * Migrated to .NET 8 and Avalonia UI 11.
  * Replaced Win32 API calls with xdotool for mouse/keyboard input.
  * Replaced Windows.Storage paths with XDG-compliant directories.
  * Replaced PowerShell script support with bash (.sh) scripts.
  * Replaced Registry-based startup with ~/.config/autostart desktop entry.
  * Added IInputProvider abstraction layer for future Wayland support.

 -- Move Mouse <contact@movemouse.co.uk>  Sat, 05 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
